  <purpose
           value="This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `Ingredient` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`Ingredient` 0..* `Ingredient`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `Ingredient` 0..* `Ingredient`

Following are the generation technical comments:
FHIR R5 Resource `Ingredient` is representable via FHIR R4 Resource `Basic`.
Element `Ingredient` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `Ingredient` is not mapped."/>
